item.title: CVE-2022-4676|2024-08-03T01:48:39.653Z -- unknown -- osm
item.description: The OSM WordPress plugin through 6.01 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
